{"TopicId":81864,"ForumId":21,"TopicTitle":"Four-legged walking robot ala Boston Dynamics\u0026#039; BIG DOG","CreatedByName":"Parallax","CreatedById":104180,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-08-16T04:56:49Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Parallax","CreatedById":104180,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-08-16T04:56:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022 contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Ciframe width=\u0022480\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/BlaCG_3FqFw?feature=oembed\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003Ethis is a proof-of-concept model, many issues yet to be resolved...\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222014-08-16T17:04:27Z\u0022 title=\u002208/16/2014 05:04  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00229 yr\u0022\u003EAugust 16, 2014\u003C/time\u003E by Parallax\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"nli2work","CreatedById":106805,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-08-16T05:00:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003Ewhats your secret? Infernal Robotics? \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Parallax","CreatedById":104180,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-08-16T05:06:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EInfernal Robotics/Tweakscale/Mechjeb \u002B custom Autohotkey script\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Darren9","CreatedById":58062,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-08-16T05:14:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EUtterly brilliant. Are you just activating action groups with Autohotkey? I\u0027ve got Autoit (a Autohotkey branch) but decided to do it in kOS because I though there could be some input lag from outside KSP, have you noticed any?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Parallax","CreatedById":104180,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-08-16T17:10:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003Ethe legs are controlled individually; there are 8 IR hotkeys total for the legs, 2 per leg. I experimented with walking manually to figure out the order in which to move the legs, then scripted it out with autohotkey. If you look closely you will see that I am actually using two different gaits; at the beginning im moving 1 leg at a time, then switch to moving two diagonally-opposite legs at once, which will be the \u0022fast moving gait\u0022 once I figure out the timing.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003Edidn\u0027t notice any input lag\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222014-08-16T17:12:44Z\u0022 title=\u002208/16/2014 05:12  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00229 yr\u0022\u003EAugust 16, 2014\u003C/time\u003E by Parallax\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"HafCoJoe","CreatedById":80363,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-08-16T17:16:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EAh! It WAS based on that video! I knew it. This thing is pretty awesome.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"nli2work","CreatedById":106805,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-08-16T21:01:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003Epretty awesome, to say the least!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Parallax","CreatedById":104180,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-08-18T02:13:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://www.gfycat.com/EnlightenedVibrantDrake#?format=gif\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://www.gfycat.com/EnlightenedVibrantDrake#?format=gif\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://www.gfycat.com/OffensiveImpishCoral\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://www.gfycat.com/OffensiveImpishCoral\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://giant.gfycat.com/EnlightenedVibrantDrake.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022EnlightenedVibrantDrake.gif\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://giant.gfycat.com/OffensiveImpishCoral.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022OffensiveImpishCoral.gif\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003Eupgraded for all-terrain use\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222014-08-18T03:02:09Z\u0022 title=\u002208/18/2014 03:02  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00229 yr\u0022\u003EAugust 18, 2014\u003C/time\u003E by Parallax\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Parallax","CreatedById":104180,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-08-23T20:24:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/GFqE7bq.png\u0022 alt=\u0022GFqE7bq.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003Elarge version coming along very nicely\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}